des:
Enjoy using voice commands to control your smart home devices with Alexa.
Follow the below steps to link Lumive skill with Alexa:
Download and install "Lumive" app from the app store then register an account;
Setup your smart devices in "Lumive" app then change devices names as you wish;
Download "Alexa" app from the Android, iOS, or Amazon app stores, then configure your "echo" in "Alexa" app;
Search "Lumive" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
Enable "Lumive" skill, and you'll be navigated to "Lumive" login page;
Complete the linking by following the instructions on the login page.
Now all the setup is finished. You can enjoy voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%”
